            <p> ll.7, 9, 10. The restorations are by Paris and Holleaux, with a modification in 1. 10 where Reinach and Robert corrected ἐνταφ[ῆναι to ἐνταφ[ήν after the discovery of 529.</p>
            <p>l.8:Supplement by L. Robert. </p>
            <p>ll. 11 ff. are conjectured from 529.</p>
